PersonalMission.Name: HT-11: Not Even a Scratch!
PersonalMission.Description: Every module destroyed and crew member injured can become a problem. Try to keep them as safe as possible when breaking through the enemy ranks.
PersonalMission.Hint: Use a First Aid Kit or a Repair Kit if the enemy destroys a key module of your vehicle or injures a crew member.

Primary.Conditions:
•  Cause 4,000 HP of damage
•  At the end of the battle, have no injured crew members or damaged/destroyed internal modules
